          Finally, a productivity app<br>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600">
            designed for ADHD minds
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Stop fighting your brain. Start working with it. PlanMyDay helps freelancers with ADHD 
          focus on what matters today—without the overwhelm.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <%= link_to "Start Free Today", new_registration_path, 
              class: "inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-medium rounded-xl text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition-all transform hover:scale-105" %>
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-purple-600 text-lg font-medium rounded-xl text-purple-600 bg-white hover:bg-purple-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition-all">
            See How It Works
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">No credit card required • Free forever for basic use</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Animated decoration -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-40 -mt-40 w-80 h-80 bg-purple-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-blob"></div>
