            <span class="text-purple-600">Brain Dump</span> Everything
          </h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Racing thoughts? Get them out fast. Voice or text, no organizing needed. 
            We'll help you process them later when you're ready.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Voice-to-text for capturing thoughts at the speed of ADHD</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>No pressure to organize—just dump and go</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>AI helps process dumps into actionable tasks later</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Daily Focus -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center mb-20 gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
