              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Only <span class="text-blue-600">3-5 Tasks</span> Per Day
          </h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            No more overwhelming lists. We limit your daily tasks to what's actually 
            achievable, helping you build momentum instead of guilt.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Hard limit prevents overcommitment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Unfinished tasks automatically roll over</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Visual progress that actually feels achievable</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Gamification -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-20 gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Your Progress</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Level 12 Productivity Wizard</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">847</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">points</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm">🔥 Current Streak</span>
                  <span class="font-bold text-orange-600">5 days</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
                  <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🏆</div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium">New Achievement!</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Task Master: Complete 50 tasks</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
                  <span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl">🌟</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl opacity-30">🏅</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl opacity-30">💎</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            <span class="text-green-600">Instant Rewards</span> That Hit Different
          </h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Get that dopamine hit your brain craves. Points, streaks, and achievements 
            make productivity feel like a game you actually want to play.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Immediate rewards for every action</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Visual celebrations that feel genuinely good</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Streak tracking to build consistent habits</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: Focus Mode -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-blue-500 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Focus Session Active</h4>
              <p class="text-purple-100 mb-4">Working on: Client proposal draft</p>
              <div class="text-5xl font-mono text-center mb-4">14:32</div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <button class="w-full px-4 py-2 bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                  Pause Timer
                </button>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <button class="flex-1 px-3 py-1 bg-yellow-500/20 hover:bg-yellow-500/30 rounded text-sm">
                    😵 Interrupted (2)
                  </button>
                  <button class="flex-1 px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/20 hover:bg-red-500/30 rounded text-sm">
                    End Session
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h4 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            <span class="text-indigo-600">Pomodoro Timer</span> Built In
          </h4>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Time blindness is real. Our built-in timer with visual countdown and 
            notifications keeps you aware without anxiety.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Visual timer you can't ignore</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Track interruptions without judgment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 mr-2">✓</span>
              <span>Gentle notifications when time's up</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">
        Why I Built PlanMyDay
      </h3>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <%= image_tag "founder.jpg", alt: "Founder of PlanMyDay", class: "w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg border-4 border-purple-100" %>
          </div>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 flex-1">
          <p class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Hi, I'm a freelancer with ADHD.</span> 
            Like you, I've tried every productivity app out there. ToDoist, Notion, Asana, Trello... 
            they all made me feel more overwhelmed, not less.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            My ADHD brain doesn't work in neat categories and endless lists. It works in bursts of 
            hyperfocus, random brilliant ideas at 2 AM, and the constant struggle of "what should I 
            be doing right now?" Traditional productivity apps made me feel broken because I couldn't 
            fit into their systems.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">So I built PlanMyDay for myself.</span> 
            An app that limits my daily tasks so I don't get overwhelmed. That lets me dump racing 
            thoughts without organizing them first. That gives me immediate rewards for completing 
            tasks because my ADHD brain needs that dopamine hit to stay motivated.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            After using it for a few months, my productivity transformed. I was actually completing 
            my daily goals. My clients were happier. I felt less anxious and more in control. 
            Friends with ADHD who saw it begged me to let them use it too.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-600">
            This isn't just another productivity app. It's built by someone with ADHD, for people 
            with ADHD. Because we deserve tools that work with our brains, not against them.
          </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-center text-gray-500">
            — Built with 💜 by someone who gets it
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Ready to Work <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600">With</span> Your ADHD?
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Join thousands of freelancers who've finally found a productivity system that works for their brain.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
        <%= link_to "Start Free Today", new_registration_path, 
            class: "inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-medium rounded-xl text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition-all transform hover:scale-105" %>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        No credit card required • Free forever for basic use • Cancel anytime
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
